## MCP Result → Java Annotation Map

|MCP finding                          |Java code                                                      |
|-------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
|Collection name `"orders"`           |`@Document(collection = "orders")`                             |
|Field `"user_id"` in document        |`@Field("user_id") private String userId;`                     |
|Single index on `user_id`            |`@Indexed` on the `userId` field                               |
|Unique index on `email`              |`@Indexed(unique = true) private String email;`                |
|Compound index `{status,created_at}` |`@CompoundIndex(def = "{'order_status':1,'created_at':-1}")`   |
|TTL index `expireAfterSeconds: 86400`|`@Indexed(expireAfterSeconds = 86400)`                         |
|Text index on `description`          |`@TextIndexed private String description;`                     |
|Nested object `"address": {...}`     |`private ShippingAddress shippingAddress;` (POJO, no @Document)|
|Array of objects `"items": [{...}]`  |`private List<LineItem> lineItems;` (POJO list, no @Document)  |
|String ID ref `"user_id": "64abc..."`|`private String userId;` + join in service                     |
|$group result: PENDING/SHIPPED/DONE  |`enum Status { PENDING, SHIPPED, DONE }`                       |
|count > 10,000                       |Add `Pageable pageable` to all repo methods                    |